Alvin Ing https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alvin_Ing 0 Alvin Ing (born May 26, 1932) is an American singer and actor. His career has included movies, television, musical theatre, and cabaret acts. Ing was born in Honolulu, Hawaii. He studied music at the University of Hawaii, and at Columbia University in New York. Alvin_Ing ( born May_26_,_1932 ) is an_American_singer_and_actor .
